name: cohsf-software-mac-intel
tagline: Office Applications and Software used by the Coalition on Homelessness, San Francisco
body:
Welcome to the Software Repository of the Coalition on Homelessness, San Francisco

This repository contains both open source and proprietary software and is intended as a central backup location for the organizations office software. We assume no responsibility for the download and installation of unlicensed and therefore illegal software. 

Below are links to all social media sites maintained by the Coalition and the Street Sheet.

[COHSF Website](http://www.cohsf.org)

[Street Sheet Temporary Website](http://streetsheetsf.wordpress.com)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
